OL,3,CMan who fled to Bulgaria convicted of
OL,4,C'vile' sexual assault of teenage girl
OL,6,FA man who fled the country after being
OL,7,Farrested for sexually assaulting a
OL,8,Fteenage girl has been brought to
OL,9,Fjustice after being extradited from
OL,10,FBulgaria.
OL,12,FShahid Hussain, 48, left the UK after
OL,13,Fbeing charged in 2018 over an attack
OL,14,Fon a 14-year-old in Rotherham 21 years
OL,15,Fago.
OL,17,FHussain drove his teenage victim down
OL,18,Fa road in 2003, parked up and led her
OL,19,Faway from the car where he forced her
OL,20,Fto perform sexual acts on him.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
