OL,3,CMan who fled to Bulgaria convicted of
OL,4,C'vile' sexual assault of teenage girl
OL,6,FHe went missing having been arrested
OL,7,Fas part of Operation Stovewood, an
OL,8,Finvestigation into child sexual
OL,9,Fexploitation in the town between 1997
OL,10,Fand 2013.
OL,12,FBut a European Arrest Warrant led to
OL,13,FHussain being arrested in Bulgaria in
OL,14,FNovember 2023.
OL,16,FAfter a trial at Sheffield Crown
OL,17,FCourt, he was found guilty of one
OL,18,Fcount of indecent assault.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
