OL,3,CMan who fled to Bulgaria convicted of
OL,4,C'vile' sexual assault of teenage girl
OL,6,FMartin McRobb, of the Crown
OL,7,FProsecution Service, said: "Shahid
OL,8,FHussain targeted a child and subjected
OL,9,Fher to a horrendous sexual assault. He
OL,10,Fthen sought to evade the law by
OL,11,Fleaving the country.
OL,13,F"I hope this conviction sends a clear
OL,14,Fmessage: sex offenders who flee abroad
OL,15,Fwill not escape justice. We will
OL,16,Fcontinue to work collaboratively with
OL,17,Finternational partners to ensure
OL,18,Fperpetrators are returned to face the
OL,19,Ffull force of the law."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
