OL,3,CMan who fled to Bulgaria convicted of
OL,4,C'vile' sexual assault of teenage girl
OL,6,FStuart Cobb, senior investigator at
OL,7,Fthe National Crime Agency, added:
OL,8,F"Hussain carried out a vile attack on
OL,9,Fa vulnerable young girl and when he
OL,10,Fknew he was going to be held to
OL,11,Faccount, he took the coward's route by
OL,12,Fgoing on the run.
OL,14,F"We have always been determined to put
OL,15,FHussain before the courts. Finally, 21
OL,16,Fyears after carrying out his crime, he
OL,17,Fhas faced justice.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
