OL,3,CMan who fled to Bulgaria convicted of
OL,4,C'vile' sexual assault of teenage girl
OL,6,F"The effects of child sexual abuse are
OL,7,Fdeep and long-lasting but I hope that
OL,8,FHussain's conviction provides the
OL,9,Fvictim with a degree of closure."
OL,11,FHussain is due to be sentenced at
OL,12,FSheffield Crown Court on 16 August.
